Both demon and heathen bring about a fall from Heaven’s grace through the worship of a false idol.
A tribe of heathens, led by women and guided by the devils below, use the Idol of Souls to bring forth an army of the fallen.
Many fell, but the brave took it upon themselves to destroy the idol to regain favor in the eyes of Yahweh. For those that diverted their gaze gained salvation.

The woman is looking for me. She was not an angel, but a demon.
I can not run and now I've made too many enemies. I will face her alone.
If you read this note, then I have failed. You must stop Madalyn.
She has opened a rift to Hell and I fear she may have the ability to bring a monster into our world.
No demon can pass through the rift without a human body. I do not know what her plan is.
There is no time to figure it out. I must be ready. I must defeat her when she arrives.
I hear her now. She is in the church.
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Her DNA was on his body… But this confirms it. She was with him the moment he died.");
